     * Who we are

     * 350 collaborateurs au service des victimes

     * Acting on behalf of victims in the name of national solidarity
     * The Guarantee Fund management committee
     * The missions of compensation
     * The recourse against the authors
     * The governance of the Guarantee Fund

     Deux structures au service des victimes
     * Guarantee Fund for victims of terrorism and other criminal acts
       (FGTI)

     * The history of FGTI
     * The missions of compensation of FGTI
     * The regulations of FGTI
     * The Board of Directors of the FGTI

     Mandatory Third-Party Liability Insurance Guarantee Fund (FGAO)
     * The history of FGAO
     * The missions of compensation of FGAO
     * The regulations of FGAO
     * The Board of Directors of the FGAO
     * The prevention

     Un organisme en transformation

     * The Guarantee Fund corporate project

     You have been a victim ?

     * Victim of an offence
     * Of an act of terrorism

     * Act of terrorism in France
     * Act of terrorism abroad and you are a Franch national

     Of a traffic accident

     * In France

     * Traffic accident caused by a vehicule registered in France
     * Traffic accident caused by a vehicule registered abroad
     * Traffic accident in a public area caused by something other than a
       motor vehicle

     Abroad

     Of another damage

     * Bankruptcy of an insurance company
     * Hunting accident
     * Mining risks
     * Technological risks

