   You have been victim

     of an offence

     of an act
   of terrorism
     * in France
     * abroad
       and you are a French national

     of a traffic accident
     * in France
          + caused by a vehicle registered in France
          + caused by a vehicle registered abroad
          + accident in a public area caused by something other than a
            motor vehicleⓘ
     * abroad

     of another
   damageⓘ
     * bankruptcy of an insurance company
     * hunting accident
     * mining risks
     * technological risks

   FGTI
   The Guarantee Fund
   for Victims of Terroriste and Other Criminal Acts
   30 years of providing
   support to victims of terrorism

   See more

   FGAO
   The Mandatory Third Party Liability Insurance
   Guarantee Fund
   65 years of experiences of working
   to help victims of traffic accidents

   See more

